SUBJECT:

Proposed Amendment to COMEX Aluminum Supplement No. 1 &Official List of

Approved Brands and Markings.8


The Exchange proposes to amend COMEX Aluminum Supplement No. 1 &Official List

of Approved Brands and Markings.8


The proposed amendment reflects the addition of NSA Ltd.,s aluminum brand

&NSA8 as acceptable for delivery against the New York Mercantile Exchange,

Inc. Aluminum Futures Contract.


The proposed amendment must be approved by the Commodity Futures Trading

Commission.В  The Exchange Membership will be notified upon receipt of CFTC

approval and the effective date of the amendment.


A copy of the proposed amendment is attached.В  Asterisks indicate additions.


